    <abstract>
      <t>This document discusses how to use the Proxy Mobile IPv6 (PMIP)
   protocol for distributed mobility management. Specifically, we
   describe the two schemes of distributed mobility management: Signal-
   driven PMIP (S-PMIP) and Signal-driven Distributed PMIP (SD-PMIP).</t>
    </abstract>
